data.description: Welcome to your slice of paradise on this beautiful 8.6-acre property! Nestled between Colorado Springs and Pueblo, this charming home offers the best of both worlds – a peaceful country setting with easy access to city amenities.    Step inside and feel right at home in the cozy living room, complete with a modern gas fireplace that's perfect for chilly evenings. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly into the dining area and kitchen, creating a warm and inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining friends.    You'll love cooking in the updated kitchen, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a gas range. Don't forget the corner pantry that offers ample storage! It's the ideal setup for preparing delicious meals while staying connected with your loved ones.    After a long day, retreat to the primary suite for some well-deserved relaxation. With a spacious walk-in closet, vanity area, and luxurious soaking tub, it's your own private sanctuary. Don't forget about the 3 additional bedrooms that offer ample space and storage in the closets.     Outside, the expansive property offers endless possibilities for outdoor fun and relaxation. Whether you're exploring the acres of land, tending to your garden, or simply enjoying the fresh air, there's something for everyone to love.    Come experience the joy of country living in this charming home. With its modern updates and serene surroundings, it's the perfect place to call your own. Welcome home!
